## Before Submitting an Update

- Every description is 100 words or less (script will check).
- Deadlines are accurate; flag "verify on official site" if unclear.
- No closed or ineligible calls in the Opportunities sheet.
- Every row has a gender category.
- File saves properly (if Excel says it’s locked, close other uses).

A well-kept tracker makes it easy for the team to see which calls fit us, their deadlines, and if FairBanks qualifies.
